{"tid":366200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凝聚力量 比叫五毛死全家更重","createTime":"2017-08-19T21:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T05:01:26.000Z","uid":16951,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4fb8cb180078a18f903e63d85673a34dae8f56","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:13:48.000Z","msg":"近排連登嘅5毛慢慢出現<br />\n個個都話見一個block一個<br />\n細佬我其實就覺得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛都可以五毛得有道理</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為咁樣先會激發大家思考 不過好明顯大部份都係<span style=\"color: red;\">偷換概念 無中生有 一嚟就屌老母</span><br />\n而對立嘅我地 都好應該反思下自己嘅回應 <br />\n一嚟就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母臭閪 死全家</span><br />\n野蠻對野蠻 根本唔治本 最應該係慢慢出post或者回應逐漸令五毛唔再五毛 而唔係自己都惡埋一份 <br />\n係我地話要民主 話要港獨 團結 但無可能每次都係有人揸大旗搞個活動先嚟團結 <br />\n我相信論壇自然可以慢慢凝聚力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">惡意批評/假膠嗰班 Block曬就啱</span><br />\n---------------<br />\n或者你因為大型抗爭嘅失敗而對今日嘅抗爭失去信心 所以唔參與<br />\n都希望你喺自己能力範圍內盡分綿力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭只係其中一部份 仲有好多方面嘅配合先會令到成件事更完滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199b836c8cce0f205567a5c20fe1e805ca596866","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064ae885b042f5ea18f6661b1e8f00b8b5779bd3","tid":366200,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:17:53.000Z","msg":"索性搞個反滲透，去支那d forum講佢地D衰野仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b739696f013a5c7399363471d051a9511e4b30ee","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索性搞個反滲透，去支那d forum講佢地D衰野仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢方面其實我地輸曬 中國人嘅玻璃心係令到佢地好易為國而憤 一齊屌尻你<br />\n你comment完 比班大陸仔鬧 你最多咪post喺道話激到佢地扎扎跳 實則你係比佢地撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2074ea229ed12cf1cf342054de8b344eabafe3","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:23:12.000Z","msg":"訓前一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e45f5b215493fe25068a78580b3426ce502779a","tid":366200,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T22:05:28.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人覺得可以講得掂班五毛<br />\n人地收晒錢做野架 邊個同你逐漸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c9c3f93e62fd529e7d4f2b858a646e5559d6f2","tid":366200,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索性搞個反滲透，去支那d forum講佢地D衰野仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔係一個懷嘅主意，只係好快俾政府mon走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f25b21b3c806a08cc2f4dd5dbaeceaa647330e3","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解仲有人覺得可以講得掂班五毛<br />\n人地收晒錢做野架 邊個同你逐漸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總好過互相無理謾罵 企返出件事睇兩邊都好似無知識咁<br />\n我地話要民主 要獨立 理應係對呢啲概念有相應嘅認識 但係一嚟就屌人老母閪 某程度上我地都係搞緊分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw都係嗰句<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無理五毛/假膠係應該block</span><br />\n收錢嗰啲會係咩質素咪就係要比人block嘅嗰種質素囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ada1ac7cd7c2023e6ade71db1bd8e6d5ee597a1","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa86166c4fbfba027c6ea8838094b06ed86cab4e","tid":366200,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB